high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island, hanging a left to reach the stove.
Pick up the teapot on the left from the stovetop.
Turn right and hang a right to reach the sink.
Rinse the teapot in the sink.
Turn to face the cabinets under the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the teapot in the farthest right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a teapot to put it away under the counter.

high_descs: pick up kettle on left side of stove top
wash kettle in sink, remove kettle from sink
walk to the right to face cabinets to right of sink
put kettle inside bottom right cabinet
anns.task_desc: put washed kettle into kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Walk right around the kitchen island, then veer left to the stove.
Pick up the leftmost kettle on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the kettle off in the sink.
Place the kettle in the bottom right cabinet, near the corner of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed kettle in a cabinet.
